Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.44,0:00:09.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Kagami Yoshimizu Theater"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.27,0:00:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.88,0:00:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.88,0:00:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grr!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.52,0:00:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit screwing around and start!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.40,0:00:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The ambiguous 3cm?\NDoes that mean it's plushy? Wait!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.40,0:00:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The wrapping is a uniform, argh,\Nit's not an act, pooh{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.57,0:00:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gotta do your best, gotta just do it{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.29,0:00:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's time to catch 'n' release, eek{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.91,0:00:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Between sweat (whoop)\NSweat (whoop){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.73,0:00:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Darlin', darlin', freeze! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.59,0:00:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kinda lethargic,\Nsomething's kinda comin' out{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.00,0:00:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I love you... Oh wait,\None of those was different{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.92,0:00:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Worrywarts, high metal bars {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.20,0:00:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tasty thoughts... And that's enough!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.93,0:00:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The heated body of that\Nflying you-know-who{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.72,0:00:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's what you call a normal girlie{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.43,0:00:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Am I the only one surprised? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.60,0:00:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Seconds on pork-bone broth ramen\Nwith wire-hard noodles{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.77,0:00:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Da da da da da {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.98,0:00:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pom-poms cheer squad{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.77,0:00:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's get cherry pie {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.37,0:00:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Happy fun welcoming party {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.87,0:00:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Look up! Sensation{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.46,0:00:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah! Feeling of existence,\Ndot dot small planet{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.58,0:00:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Collided and it melted away,\Nin total awe{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.20,0:01:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go all out to sing, shi-ranger!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.91,0:01:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Take it away! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.12,0:01:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I should be the one who'll be\Nlaughing in the end{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.49,0:01:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because I have the sailor suit\N← This is my conclusion{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.51,0:01:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's only Monday! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.82,0:01:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Already in a bad mood? What to do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.37,0:01:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I really prefer the summer outfits\N← kya! Wah! Good! (cute!) < 3{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.14,0:01:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Until we approach 3 pixels,\Nno hesitations please ★{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.39,0:01:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Do your best, be energetic {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.02,0:01:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My darlin', darlin' please! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.44,0:01:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. It's so smelly!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.59,0:01:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So smelly!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.58,0:01:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Golden Week is almost over now,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.34,0:01:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but are you two all right\Nwith homework and stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.25,0:01:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I'm not done yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.89,0:01:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tend to play away these long\Nholidays. We're in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.18,0:01:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.65,0:01:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I'm acutally\Nalmost all done with mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.20,0:02:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were playing with me\Nall this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.97,0:02:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Efforts and Results"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.23,0:02:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.92,0:02:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was talking about this one...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.51,0:02:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I would understand\Nsomething that baffles you, Kagami!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.70,0:02:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in college, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.08,0:02:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go and wake Tsukasa up already.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.26,0:02:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to.\NShe won't wake up, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.16,0:02:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.19,0:02:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad sure is late.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.20,0:02:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was he at the groundbreaking\Nceremony this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.56,0:02:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What time is it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.07,0:02:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.76,0:02:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's already past noon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.12,0:02:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.15,0:02:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.56,0:02:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.88,0:02:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you sleep so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.20,0:03:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see the special finale\Nof {\i1}Love Apron {\i0}last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.22,0:03:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I missed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.08,0:03:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I fell asleep halfway...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.58,0:03:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you slept through it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.06,0:03:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was an amazing turn of events!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.09,0:03:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the very end, a guy with\Na red basin on his head...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.83,0:03:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagami, you have\Na phone call from Miyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.25,0:03:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.60,0:03:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to hold a study session
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.84,0:03:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that doubles as\Na homework answer check?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.56,0:03:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that sounds good.\NLet's do it, let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.16,0:03:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagami, you have\Na phone call from Konata.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.53,0:03:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to hold a study session
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.60,0:03:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that doubles as a homework cleanup?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.02,0:03:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute! In your case, all\Nyou do is copy all my homework!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, I would like to\Ncopy your homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.29,0:03:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're awfully straightforward.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.78,0:03:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right for you to\Ncopy my homework,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.15,0:03:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but if you don't do it all by yourself,\Nyou're going to have
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.45,0:03:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,horrible scores on the first exam\Nafter break, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.01,0:03:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true... It won't be\Nfor my own good...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.75,0:03:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine, because I'm good at\Nthe one-night cram session.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.91,0:03:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, show it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.58,0:04:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should worry at least a little bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.27,0:04:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.44,0:04:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh, welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.86,0:04:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.38,0:04:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, are you part of the study group\Nas well, Izumi-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.04,0:04:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, she's flat-out copying everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.75,0:04:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, you haven't\Ndone anything at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.22,0:04:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you doing\Nduring the break?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.10,0:04:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.19,0:04:21.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Day 1"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.44,0:04:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,23 pages of math,\N20 pages of world history,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.25,0:04:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,30 pages of English...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.64,0:04:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The break is five days long.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.83,0:04:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So if I think I'll study for five--\Nno, four hours a day...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.65,0:04:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Math goes at 1.15 pages per hour...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.20,0:04:39.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Day 2"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.76,0:04:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, I haven't done anything today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.35,0:04:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... I have three days left,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.26,0:04:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I guess I'll work six hours a day...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.85,0:04:50.01,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Day 3"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.21,0:04:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The coworker who has been working\Nunder me for the past ten years
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.41,0:04:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,still doesn't remember my name...\NI am Yutaka... I am Yutaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.80,0:04:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two more days...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.16,0:04:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I work frantically for\Nthe next two days...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.31,0:04:59.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Day 4"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.83,0:05:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Golden Week is almost over now,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.64,0:05:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but are you two all right\Nwith homework and stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.19,0:05:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to hold a study session
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.50,0:05:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that doubles as a homework cleanup?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.16,0:05:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought about doing them all\Nas I initially planned...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.76,0:05:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The plan fell flat on its face.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.27,0:05:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your resistance was futile.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.87,0:05:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're worse off than she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.03,0:05:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, she tried her best\Nand did it on her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.47,0:05:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deep down, she's very\Nserious about her work,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.16,0:05:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no matter what people say.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.35,0:05:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But her accuracy is so bad\Nthat I can't bear to look.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.08,0:05:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So horrible... just so horrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.15,0:05:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.43,0:05:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you able to spend\Nthe short vacation in a fun way?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.19,0:05:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then, you had quite\Na bit of homework,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.15,0:05:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you get a midterm\Nthe day you come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.15,0:05:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you couldn't have been\Nfooling around the entire break!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.20,0:05:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't feel like I had a break at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.13,0:05:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, sorry to say,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.04,0:05:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I didn't let any of that worry me,\Nand I played around!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.08,0:05:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma'am...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.97,0:05:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.48,0:05:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't let anything worry me,\Nand I played around too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.56,0:06:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.87,0:06:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought things like that were made\Nso that you could never get them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.91,0:06:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It depends on the item.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.28,0:06:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a few things that are\Nmade to be difficult to get.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.16,0:06:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right? That's why\NI don't feel like trying them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.77,0:06:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.64,0:06:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this one was an easy target.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.99,0:06:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.94,0:06:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's that one,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.08,0:06:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,maybe even if it was me trying,\Nperhaps it will tumble...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.29,0:06:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"...and I'll be able to get it,"\Nis what you were thinking, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.68,0:06:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, I'm not thinking\Nof anything of the sort.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.04,0:06:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But maybe I'll try just this once?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.30,0:06:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go for it, Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.61,0:06:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I had that one for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.25,0:06:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.48,0:06:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.48,0:06:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.40,0:06:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A wise man once said,\N"UFO catchers are piggy banks."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.74,0:06:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.81,0:07:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, again... No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.27,0:07:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Announcing the results!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.56,0:07:09.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--I was no good at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.88,0:07:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You are at Taiko Entry Level 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.36,0:07:12.46,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--Kona-{\i1}chan{\i0}, you have a \Nvery good sense of rhythm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.84,0:07:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You are at Taiko Black Belt Level 5!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.46,0:07:14.70,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--No, a sense of rhythm \Ndoesn't matter at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.00,0:07:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The skills you get by gaming are\Nusually useless in everyday life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.16,0:07:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see that clearly\Nwhen I look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.88,0:07:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kona-{\i1}chan{\i0}, you're so strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.56,0:07:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.72,0:07:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much money has she\Nfed into this thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.57,0:07:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Izumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.04,0:07:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Izumi absent today?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.17,0:07:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kuroi, a phone call from Izumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.36,0:07:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, this is Kuroi speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.31,0:08:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Ma'am, I'm sorry, but I\Nwant to call in sick today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.39,0:08:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, Izumi? This is unusual for you.\NDid you catch a cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.04,0:08:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I have May sickness...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.60,0:08:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sluggish.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.67,0:08:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and get over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.65,0:08:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, we're going home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.12,0:08:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you stuffing\Nyour bag like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.19,0:08:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the exams start tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.95,0:08:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to take everything home\Nwith me today to study overnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.15,0:08:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you kept every textbook here\Nand studied only in school!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.98,0:08:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief, there's no way\Nyou'd make it in time
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.37,0:08:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if you're taking all\Nyour textbooks home
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.07,0:08:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,only on the night before the exams!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.12,0:08:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've always\Nmade it through like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.70,0:08:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.58,0:08:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll see how far\Nyou can go with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.50,0:08:43.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"First Semester Midterms"\N"Modern Literature" "Math" "English"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.27,0:08:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'm gonna return\Nthe exams you took the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.64,0:08:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.01,0:09:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.54,0:09:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like, don't ask me...\NThough I did my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.77,0:09:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, how about that all-nighter girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.89,0:09:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to my studying,\NI had it down pat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.37,0:09:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.35,0:09:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lucky Star{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.94,0:09:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So sluggish... I don't feel\Nlike doing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.96,0:09:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, we're going home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.36,0:09:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite what you say,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.72,0:09:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you always hang out with us\Nwhen we make these stops.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.58,0:09:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Comp-Fest!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.31,0:09:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,QUO Cards for everyone who fills out \Nthe order! I have to get them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.25,0:09:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I guess it's time\Nto get a part-time job!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.40,0:09:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are a simple person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.26,0:09:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, I've never heard of anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.39,0:09:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who tried to call in sick\Nwith May sickness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.47,0:09:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I understand how it feels...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.53,0:09:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They call it a sickness,\Nso it's a legit excuse, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.23,0:09:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying that seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.81,0:09:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.34,0:09:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, what exactly is\Nthe May sickness, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.52,0:09:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki, explain it to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.73,0:09:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.07,0:09:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the sense of accomplishment\Nof meeting a large goal,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.96,0:10:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,like school entrance exams\Nor successfully being hired,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.24,0:10:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or the difficulties in having\Ninterpersonal relationships
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.15,0:10:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with people you meet starting in April,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.62,0:10:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or the inability to adjust to the gap\Nbetween ideals and reality
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.24,0:10:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when it comes to the new life\Nyou started to live,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.68,0:10:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there is a sense of apathy,\Nor downright depression.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.98,0:10:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, if it's just that\Nyour body feels sluggish,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.85,0:10:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if you can\Nreally call it May sickness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.44,0:10:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the first place,\Nwe're all in eleventh grade,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.00,0:10:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so that doesn't apply to us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.84,0:10:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always do my best with a fresh\Nheart in the spring every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.87,0:10:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.42,0:10:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not just Konata.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.39,0:10:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really tend to get sluggish\Nat this time of the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.08,0:10:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when you get home,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.60,0:10:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you just don't feel up to\Ndoing homework and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.92,0:10:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.23,0:10:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel too lazy to make\Nthe comeback, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.45,0:10:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Yuki-{\i1}chan{\i0}?\NYou're sighing and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.09,0:10:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm embarrassed to talk about this,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.39,0:10:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just like when I talked\Nabout contact lenses.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.84,0:10:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've been too afraid\Nto go to the dentist,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.27,0:10:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and my cavity is getting\Nworse and worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.97,0:11:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so bad now that it stings\Neven when I drink water.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.61,0:11:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.58,0:11:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid of them too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.10,0:11:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why did you let it get this bad
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.40,0:11:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before going to the dentist?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.68,0:11:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's very strange,\Nbut even though I knew
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.84,0:11:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that it would be tough for me\Nwhen my teeth started to hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.10,0:11:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For some reason, you don't\Nwant to go to the dentist.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.72,0:11:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even after the pain starts,\Nwhile you can withstand it,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.43,0:11:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you tend to choose not to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.42,0:11:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are dentists really that scary?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.58,0:11:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know because I've\Nnever had to deal with one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.67,0:11:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've never gone to one?\NI'm so jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.08,0:11:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That distinct antiseptic smell\Nin the dentist's office...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.79,0:11:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tension you feel\Nin the waiting room...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.17,0:11:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That, and don't forget the sound\Nof the spinning drills!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.56,0:11:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Change Getter{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.31,0:11:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.08,0:11:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But boys might like\Ndentists and stuff, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.32,0:11:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.98,0:11:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, they say that a drill\Nis like a guy's romantic ideal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.19,0:11:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dinosaur Empire{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.65,0:12:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear they're all about dueling robots\Nthat use drills as weapons!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.65,0:12:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I think they would hate\Ntheir teeth being drilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.20,0:12:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always think how so many\Nof the dental assistants
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.15,0:12:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and receptionists are so pretty...\NDon't you think so too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.21,0:12:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.40,0:12:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.01,0:12:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can it be the aesthetic standards\Nof the person hiring them?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.22,0:12:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A beautiful dental assistant\Nand a drill, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.36,0:12:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It certainly does seem to be\Ngeared more towards men.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.94,0:12:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what would a dentist\Ngeared for women be like?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.65,0:12:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First off, they'd have to get rid\Nof that smell or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.65,0:12:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the chair that they use has to be\Na fluffy reclining chair with a massage unit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.78,0:12:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'd have to add\Naromatherapy as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.61,0:12:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or have a foot massage at the same\Ntime as the dental treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.92,0:12:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.55,0:13:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That, and be able to play games\Nto ease the pain of treatment!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.87,0:13:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A game might be rather hard to play...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.96,0:13:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's a good idea to have them\Ndistract our attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.96,0:13:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like putting headphones on and\Nlistening to our favorite music.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.14,0:13:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.39,0:13:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That also sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.96,0:13:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.52,0:13:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in the end, I still don't\Nwant to go to a dentist.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.57,0:13:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.90,0:13:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.90,0:13:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.24,0:13:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, another one of my favorite\Nseries is turning into an anime,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.50,0:13:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the cast is completely\Ndifferent from the drama CD.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.76,0:13:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.15,0:13:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it the unseen hand\Nof God yet again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.83,0:13:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Politics? Or money?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.38,0:13:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not one to ever buy drama CDs,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.16,0:13:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I don't care who the cast is,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.91,0:13:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as long as the voice matches the\Ncharacter as portrayed in the original.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.84,0:13:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not how it works, Kagamin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.29,0:13:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those that are used to\Nlistening to the drama CDs
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.93,0:13:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,find it awkward when they\Nstart watching the anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.92,0:13:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it takes quite a bit of time\Nbefore that awkwardness is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.22,0:13:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.10,0:14:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, there is one good thing\Nto come out of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.44,0:14:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.36,0:14:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The drama CDs and the anime...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.16,0:14:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can enjoy two worlds\Nwith two different voices.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.96,0:14:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The same piece of candy,\Nbut twice as tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.85,0:14:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are a strong customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.99,0:14:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, one of us is going\Nto take the nugget
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.07,0:14:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that Miyuki-{\i1}san {\i0}has left uneaten...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.75,0:14:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have a staring contest\Nto decide it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.80,0:14:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? That's so childish.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.64,0:14:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A staring contest? That sounds fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.00,0:14:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I think Kagami\Nwill win, hands down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.94,0:14:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.97,0:14:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's go.\NIt's a staring contest...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.43,0:14:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blaaaaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.10,0:14:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.44,0:14:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.97,0:14:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not something\Na human can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.62,0:14:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you guys are both overreacting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.17,0:14:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I made you wait.\NThe bathroom was rather crowded...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.03,0:14:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.41,0:14:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, show that face\Nyou just made to Miyuki too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.52,0:14:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.90,0:14:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki, it was amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.68,0:15:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was a face that you've\Nnever seen before in your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.50,0:15:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.19,0:15:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so amazing no matter\Nhow many times I see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.36,0:15:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could use that face for the\Ntalent part of a college application.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.73,0:15:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Konata!\NUse that to apply for college!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.63,0:15:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you'll get accepted!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.48,0:15:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't make me so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.60,0:15:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were doing something on TV
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.32,0:15:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,like how many books an average\NJapanese person reads in a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.03,0:15:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Manga's not good enough,\Nordinary books only, please!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.16,0:15:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is what they were saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.50,0:15:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, manga is, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.61,0:15:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do light novels count?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.63,0:15:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know... Though I'd think\Nthat light novels are okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.41,0:15:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about picture books?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.90,0:15:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you say a book, you have\Nthe right sense of the word...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.50,0:15:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also for the fantasy genre,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.41,0:15:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,everyone would nod in agreement\Nif you say that {\i1}Harry Potter{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.64,0:15:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and stuff like that are ordinary books.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.08,0:15:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, what exactly\Nis an ordinary book?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.26,0:15:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, on that TV show,\Nthey ended the show saying that
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.75,0:16:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the younger generation is veering\Naway from reading on the whole.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.98,0:16:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But nowadays, we use the net
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.43,0:16:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to look at all sorts of\Nwebsites and blogs,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.58,0:16:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I think we have a higher\Npercentage of reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.72,0:16:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... I'm kinda getting it,\Nand I'm kinda not...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.49,0:16:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you two, let's go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.57,0:16:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.74,0:16:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sorry, I can't go home\Nwith you guys today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.47,0:16:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have an errand to run or\Nsomething? That's unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.75,0:16:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I started a part-time job.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.07,0:16:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.21,0:16:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, she really started\Na part-time job!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.80,0:16:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the Comp-Fest that\Nimportant to her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.91,0:16:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, you know,\NKonata really surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.00,0:16:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. She really\Nstarted a part-time job.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.60,0:16:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that she was just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.11,0:16:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That too, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.28,0:16:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was surprised that\Nanyone would hire her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.41,0:16:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a little harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.19,0:16:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't imagine her working\Ndiligently in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.68,0:16:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.20,0:16:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder where she's working.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.75,0:17:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe a bookstore or something,\Nsince she loves manga so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.87,0:17:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, can I have this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.16,0:17:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a sec. I'm too busy right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.44,0:17:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.63,0:17:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope she doesn't get fired...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.12,0:17:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about a convenience store?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.31,0:17:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, can I have this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.70,0:17:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,498yen...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.09,0:17:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Justtherightamount...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.31,0:17:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thankyouverymuch.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.60,0:17:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah... I can't see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.76,0:17:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what about a fast-food joint?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.23,0:17:30.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Smile 0 yen"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.23,0:17:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am smiling, what about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.83,0:17:32.16,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe that's impossible too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.16,0:17:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Along the same lines, a family-style\Nrestaurant is out of the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.24,0:17:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.68,0:17:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, what kind\Nof job did she get?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.71,0:17:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.90,0:17:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe counting the amount of traffic?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.78,0:17:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.53,0:17:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A video rental place?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.78,0:17:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.96,0:17:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A pub?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.79,0:17:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.87,0:17:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pizza delivery?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.76,0:17:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't have a license.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.80,0:17:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A cashier in a supermarket?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.10,0:17:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.66,0:17:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An instructor in a cram school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.57,0:17:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.32,0:17:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bread factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.20,0:17:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.75,0:17:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... What else...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.44,0:17:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just ask her tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.36,0:18:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Konata, what kind of place\Nare you working at?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.25,0:18:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, tell us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.61,0:18:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's an ordinary cosplay café.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.58,0:18:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that's so fitting for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.14,0:18:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But is that kind of place really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.31,0:18:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lucky Star{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.84,0:18:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lucky Channel{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.13,0:18:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning Luckies!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.95,0:18:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Akira Kogami! This is the\Nsecond episode of {\i1}Lucky Channel{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.72,0:18:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to do my best\Nto deliver it to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.71,0:18:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, next to me is a wonderful\Nyoung man who will assist me,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.59,0:18:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minoru Shiraishi-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.96,0:18:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... wa... wawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.69,0:18:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Minoru Shiraishi,\Nassistant to Akira-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.40,0:18:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still very new, so I hope that
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.08,0:18:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll at least remember my name\Nbefore you go home! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.09,0:18:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clap, clap, clap...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.88,0:18:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, this segment has just started,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.96,0:18:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but already messages from all of you\Nhave arrived with a bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.11,0:18:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akira's super happy! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.90,0:18:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this really is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.34,0:18:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must all be a sign of your\Npopularity, Akira-{\i1}sama{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.36,0:19:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.34,0:19:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw it today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.73,0:19:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.28,0:19:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were in it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.67,0:19:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the main show. You had a part.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.97,0:19:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I had the opportunity\Nto play a small part.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.70,0:19:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.53,0:19:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But wait? What scene were you in?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.30,0:19:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I believe it was\Nthe 45th cut of part A,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.94,0:19:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the scene in the classroom\Nright after the holiday break.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.06,0:19:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, oh, oh, I remember now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.55,0:19:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You had such a small presence\Non screen that I had forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.69,0:19:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time, I only had one line\Nin the entire scene, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.39,0:19:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?\NYou're dissatisfied by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.23,0:19:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, that's definitely not the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.73,0:19:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I don't know about\Nnewbies acting like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.64,0:19:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I first debuted...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.68,0:19:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Debut? Exactly how old were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.68,0:19:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.00,0:19:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, I was ecstatic\Njust by getting a line to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.33,0:19:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting to speak isn't about\Nthe number of lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.32,0:19:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well now, I was surrounded by all\Nthe great names in the industry,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.31,0:19:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so it was a series of tense moments.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.73,0:19:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a great learning\Nexperience for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.20,0:20:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really were tense, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.36,0:20:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were rock solid.\NA complete amateur.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.26,0:20:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, that was just\Nso you-know-what,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.81,0:20:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so how about you\Ntry again right here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.77,0:20:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, you mean right here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.73,0:20:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You might show up again\Nin a future episode, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.34,0:20:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.67,0:20:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you have to practice\Na little, at least!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.99,0:20:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you that I'm going\Nto help you out right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.72,0:20:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I understand now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.96,0:20:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in your hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.68,0:20:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me the script.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.72,0:20:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which cut was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.37,0:20:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut 45.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.44,0:20:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.74,0:20:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll play the teacher, Miss Kuroi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.07,0:20:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please do!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.11,0:20:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, ready... Action!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.95,0:20:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.85,0:20:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you able to spend\Nthe short vacation in a fun way?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.32,0:20:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then, you had q-q... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.02,0:20:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's "quite."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.87,0:20:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quite a bit of homework,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.07,0:20:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you get a midterm\Nthe day you come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.16,0:20:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you couldn't have been\Nfooling around the entire break!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.52,0:20:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't feel like I had a break at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.02,0:20:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.76,0:20:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No good at all.\NYour line just doesn't deliver.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.26,0:20:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deliver?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.87,0:21:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here! Right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.91,0:21:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't reach here at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.72,0:21:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.53,0:21:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even a monkey can do it,\Nif it's just reciting a line!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.51,0:21:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe a monkey\Nwouldn't be able to do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.16,0:21:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.78,0:21:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's already\Ntime to say goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.82,0:21:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy times really go by\Nquickly, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.46,0:21:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, please send us\Nquestions and praise for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.15,0:21:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as well as your opinions of the show!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.84,0:21:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well... We hope to see you again\Nin the next episode.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.12,0:21:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.98,0:21:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, what about it?\NThose regulars on the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.40,0:21:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By that, you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.91,0:21:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking about, how to put it,\Nlike someone being pulled down...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.08,0:21:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't they all hate each\Nother or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.19,0:21:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't think that\Nis the case right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.59,0:21:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, how about you be\Nconsiderate, and--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.68,0:21:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kona-{\i1}chan{\i0}, you're amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.43,0:21:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was very passionate!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.85,0:21:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Konata! Are there two\Nmore songs of this sort left?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.91,0:21:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I put in anime songs as well\Nas those live-action hero ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.01,0:21:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the point\NI'm trying to make!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.71,0:21:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sing songs that even\Nwe would recognize!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.06,0:22:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're free to sing whatever we want.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.73,0:22:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.59,0:22:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Tsukasa, you have\Nto punch songs in,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.78,0:22:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or we'll have to listen to an endless\Nstream of her anime songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.25,0:22:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't mind if that was the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.28,0:22:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is fun in its own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.20,0:22:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, you too, Miyuki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.87,0:22:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to get in front of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.37,0:22:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna sing standing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.58,0:22:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you up to now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.24,0:22:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't really get my voice out from\Nmy stomach if I don't stand up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.72,0:22:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to sing even louder\Nthan the last song?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.46,0:22:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's the original footage!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.15,0:22:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this is somehow quite amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.83,0:22:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This looks like something from\Nway before we were born.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.56,0:22:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have your drinks here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.57,0:22:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.04,0:22:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who ordered oolong tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.29,0:22:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.95,0:23:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who ordered iced lemon tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.58,0:23:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.79,0:23:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who ordered orange juice?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.09,0:23:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.26,0:23:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who ordered ginger ale?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.68,0:23:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please leave that one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.41,0:23:16.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Next Episode Preview"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.37,0:23:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, what's with\Nthe next episode of {\i1}Lucky Star{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.72,0:23:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagami here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.66,0:23:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I put in 200 yen to buy\Na can of juice in a vending machine
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.21,0:23:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and get one 50-yen coin and\Nsome 10-yen coins as change,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.24,0:23:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think, "I win!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.54,0:23:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But on the other hand, when I'm\Nbuying a 150-yen ticket for a train,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.36,0:23:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and after putting in a 100-yen coin,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.86,0:23:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that I have five 10-yen\Ncoins left, so I put in four,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.48,0:23:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I actually had only four\Nand am one short,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.83,0:23:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I end up putting in another\N100-yen coin to buy the ticket
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.83,0:23:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and thus get nine 10-yen\Ncoins as change...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.86,0:23:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that sense of defeat\Nis really something!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.29,0:23:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: Various People.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.35,0:23:43.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Various People"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.32,0:23:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look forward to it!
